snippet.title: Tile Cities trailer
snippet.description:
A side project of the developer of Ostriv created during war. 
Tile Cities is a minimalistic city-building puzzle game.
Beta is available at https://tilecitiesgame.com
Learn more: https://twitter.com/TileCitiesGame
